Author: Yahya Ibrahim

Author: AQ Chef'
column2:
Pseudonym given to author(s) of
the Open Source Jihad tutorials

Author: Ayman al-Zawahiri
column2:
Current leader of Al-Qaeda Central;
successor to Usama bin Laden

Author: Samir Khan
column2:
Pakistani-American ideologue
for AQAP and editor of Inspire;
killed in drone strike in 2011

Author: Usama bin Laden
column2: Founder of al-Qaeda

Author: Anwar al-Awlaki
column2:
Influential Yemeni preacher and ideologue born and educated in the United States.
Believed to have edited for Inspire. Along with Samir Khan, he was the first
American citizen to be targeted and killed in a drone strike (d. 2011).
